  "texts": [
    "An ablation study confirmed the critical contribution of the topological processing order to both helpfulness and truthfulness.",
    "DocAgent represents a promising step towards reliable and useful automated code documentation generation for complex and proprietary software.",
    "DocAgent, while advancing automated code documentation, has inherent limitations and ethical considerations.",
    "Technically, processing extremely large codebases may still challenge LLM context limits despite topological sorting and context management.",
    "Relying solely on static analysis restricts understanding of dynamic behavior, and the current Python focus requires effort for adaptation to other languages."
